<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4581254>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Hypothetical process of regeneration in Jullienipora calypsoides. (A) Intact colony. (B) Loss of the basal heterozooid of a branch. (C) Regeneration of a second peristome orientated oppositely to the original zooid (compare with Figures 2A, 3C)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4581254/files/figure.png" .

