<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4581252>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Jullienipora calypsoides. (A) MNHN-BRY-3900. A linear branch showing four heterozooids on the same side (asterisks). (B) MNHN-BRY-3749. Branching pattern. The second lateral branching is partially covered with external material (arrow). (C) MNHN-BRY-3900. A possible regeneration (compare with Figures 2A, 4)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4581252/files/figure.png" .

